{"tid":1453113,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔 麻煩出個通告要所有人檢查回覆紀錄","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:09:57.000Z","uid":259352,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea675c714c79825ca8a25334e5d4774c2886f7f","tid":1453113,"uid":259352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxgswNH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxgswNH.jpg&h=34385435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中兩個post絕對不是本人發出的<br />\n內文字海 仲要有圖，起我底就會知完全唔對路<br />\n如果有人有咁既手段 依家所有P牌會員都好大機會受害<br />\n<br />\n想建議你出個置頂post呼籲所有人檢查左先<br />\n其次 限制左P牌會員出post先 咁樣好危險！"},{"pid":"1d929d034e691d6cbb441db438548c458586cbf4","tid":1453113,"uid":259352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"救命呀 要越多人睇到先得。當大部分會員check完發現都冇事，就證明係我自己比人hack; 反之可能係有漏洞存在"},{"pid":"e79169dad81c943a42061a502e0d23d462a2ba46","tid":1453113,"uid":215206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aff8b6763da402adb3b0469b785ed7bdab1f48","tid":1453113,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"有無係其他地方login過"},{"pid":"e9813ba9b07f12eb82988ce87d692c15ebe59a30","tid":1453113,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打咁爽一獲"},{"pid":"14d3266e5c3dbeffec58ebe54f103e077577fcbb","tid":1453113,"uid":259352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4aff8b6763da402adb3b0469b785ed7bdab1f48","tid":1453113,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"有無係其他地方login過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"